 video, which was uploaded in November, now has more than 700,000 views.\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The video\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 628}, {\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 660}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 700,000 views\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The creator, Ms Miranda Starcevic, is a 31-year-old French American who lives in Paris.\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 783, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 712, \"end\": 719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miranda_warning\", \"score\": 0.999999988682248, \"rank\": 1.1317607167385572e-08, \"text\": \"Miranda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miranda_warning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miranda_warning\"}, {\"begin\": 748, \"end\": 763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 748, \"end\": 763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 777, \"end\": 782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2045953954081995e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The creator\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She usually records herself speaking in French, but thought a message about the Olympics would reach more people if it were in English.\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Frenc