m\": 1161, \"to\": 1177}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics content\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in addition to feel-good windows into athletes' lives and promotional videos from organisers and sponsors, there are also unfiltered clips from residents warning potential visitors that Paris may not deliver its best during the Games.\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1406, \"end\": 1411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2045953954081995e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"good windows\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1252}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes' lives\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1273}, {\"ngram\": \"promotional videos\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1296}, {\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1312}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsors\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"unfiltered clips\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"residents\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"potential visitors\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A 24-year-old student whose display name is Leo Nora has posted several short clips about the Paris Games, stating they will be \\\"dangerous\\\" and \\\"hell on earth\\\".\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1500, \"end\": 1503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"score\": 0.9999998112380304, \"rank\": 1.8876192924100548e-07, \"text\": \"Leo\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\"}, {\"begin\": 1504, \"end\": 1508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\", \"score\": 0.999985