ve up their student housing, so the accommodations could be used for workers during the Games.\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2150}, {\"ngram\": \"students\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2165}, {\"ngram\": \"their student housing\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2198}, {\"ngram\": \"the accommodations\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"workers\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2247}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2264}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And both expressed frustration and fears around transportation.\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"frustration\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2296}, {\"ngram\": \"fears\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2306}, {\"ngram\": \"transportation\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fares to ride on the Paris Metro will be almost doubling during the Games - a bit of Olympic surge pricing that has already caused much grumbling.\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2352, \"end\": 2363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_M\\u00e9tro\", \"score\": 0.9999998407888724, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Metro\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_M\\u00e9tro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_M\\u00e9tro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fares\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2336}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2404}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2412}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic surge pricing\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2437}, {\"ngram\": \"much grumbling\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers and government officials are concerned about strikes by transportation workers during the Games, as well as more serious issues like terrorism.\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organisers\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2489}, {\"ngram\": \"government officials\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"strikes\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2542}, {\"ngram\": \"transportation workers\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2568}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2585}, {\"ngram\": \"more serious issues\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2617}, {\"ngram\": \"terrorism\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some creators have posted about Paris' pervasive tourist scams, pickpockets and recent hotel price hikes.\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2667, \"end\": 2672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2045953954081995e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some creators\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2648}, {\"ngram\": \"pickpockets\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2710}, {\"ngram\": \"recent hotel price hikes\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2739}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People on TikTok also warned that there could be severe overcrowding on trains.\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2752, \"end\": 2758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232427750616791e-46, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2748}, {\"ngram\": \"severe overcrowding\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2810}, {\"ngram\": \"trains\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2820}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not rare to have people fainting\\\" in the Metro, Ms Leo Nora said, adding that when someone faints, \\\"the line stops, which causes delays\\\".\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2966, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2880, \"end\": 2883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"score\": 0.9999998112380304, \"rank\": 1.8876192924100548e-07, \"text\": \"Leo\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\"}, {\"begin\": 2884, \"end\": 2888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\", \"score\": 0.999985000427104, \"rank\": 1.499206239831317e-05, \"text\": \"Nora\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2846, \"to\": 2852}, {\"ngram\": \"the Metro\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2875}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2937}, {\"ngram\": \"delays\", \"from\": 2958, \"to\": 2964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ms Tessa Bicard, an executive at a cosmetics company whose TikTok handle is Madame Tartempion, posted a video titled \\\"The Olympics are going to be a nightmare for Paris\\\".\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 3138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3027, \"end\": 3033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232427750616791e-46, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}, {\"begin\": 3131, \"end\": 3136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2045953954081995e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ms Tessa Bicard\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 2983}, {\"ngram\": \"an executive\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 2997}, {\"ngram\": \"a cosmetics company\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3020}, {\"ngram\": \"Madame Tartempion\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3061}, {\"ngram\": \"