bout the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 3499, \"to\": 3578, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mainly, she said, that is because she does not have tickets.\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3640, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 3632, \"to\": 3639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are too expensive or impossible to get,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3697, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She also stressed that all the different construction projects for the Games have already made daily life difficult.\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the different construction projects\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3761}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3766, \"to\": 3775}, {\"ngram\": \"daily life\", \"from\": 3794, \"to\": 3804}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The expected influx of millions of Olympics visitors, she fears, will just make things worse.\", \"from\": 3817, \"to\": 3910, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The expected influx\", \"from\": 3817, \"to\": 3836}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 3840, \"to\": 3848}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics visitors\", \"from\": 3852, \"to\": 3869}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 3897, \"to\": 3903}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My bus route has been complete chaos.\\\"\", \"from\": 3911, \"to\": 3950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My bus route\", \"from\": 3912, \"to\": 3924}, {\"ngram\": \"complete chaos\", \"from\": 3934, \"to\": 3948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As an American living in Paris, Ms Bicard said she often uses her TikTok account to answer questions about the city, in addition to fun tips like \\\"how to spot an American in Paris\\\".\", \"from\": 3952, \"to\": 4133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3958, \"end\": 3966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9981636421152366, \"rank\": 